    public class ReorderPlaylistsItemsRequest

    Reorder an item or a group of items in a playlist.

    When reordering items, the timestamp indicating when they were added and the user who added them will be kept untouched. In addition, the users following the playlists wonâ€™t be notified about changes in the playlists when the items are reordered.
